WHEREAS, Heaven displays incredible humility and credits her successes to her
unwavering faith in God and the support she receives from her family, friends, coaches, and
mentors; and
WHEREAS, Heaven plans to attend Mississippi State University to study
broadcasting on a full four-year scholarship, and she will continue to use her voice to inspire
others and make a lasting impact; and
WHEREAS, Heaven Riley Breaux leads with grace, purpose, and a heart for service,
and she is most deserving of the highest recognition for her incredible achievements.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend Heaven Riley Breaux on being named Miss
Louisiana Teen USA and does hereby extend sincere wishes that she remain prosperous in
all of her endeavors.
